node.text:
SUPER HERO VIBES. 🌟💪✨
.
.
A HERO is somebody who is SELFLESS, who is GENEROUS in SPIRIT, who just tries to GIVE back as much as possible and HELP people. A hero to me is someone who SAVES people and who really deeply CARES
.
.
Would you consider yourself a #SuperHero ? What are some of the things you’re doing to make this world a better place? If not, How can YOU show up this week & be a real-life super hero?
.
#Qotd #WonderWoman #strength #selfless #selflove #warrior #power  #ladywarrior #santanagarrett#ig #followforfollowback #hero #believe

node.text:
Grateful. 💛
.
.
.
THANK YOU- To my SPONSORS & FANS who continue to stick around & support me despite being on tv or in action the past year or so.. 
.
THANK YOU-to my FRIENDS & FAMILY who continue to text and call me even though sometimes I fail to respond..
.
THANK YOU-to my HUSBAND & BEST FRIEND When I look back on the past 5+ years, there are a few things that are constant: your presence, your love, & your ability to see the potential in me to be GREAT even though sometimes I cannot see it for myself.
.
.
I don’t say it enough, but I am so GRATEFUL to all of you! 💛🙏✨
